<template>
  <winWheel :segments="items"></winWheel>
</template>

<script>
import VueWinwheel from "vue-winwheel-reversion/vue-winwheel";

export default {
  name: "sss-ss",
  components: {
    winWheel: VueWinwheel,
  },
  data() {
    return {
      pageTitle: "Vue-Wheel",
      wheelSize: 400,
      btnColor: "",
      btnText: "",
      lineWidth: 3,
      duration: 5,
      spin: 5,
      items: [
        {
          textFillStyle: "#fff",
          fillStyle: "#000",
          text: "Prize 1",
        },
        {
          textFillStyle: "#000",
          fillStyle: "#fadede",
          text: "Prize 2",
        },
        {
          textFillStyle: "#fff",
          fillStyle: "#000",
          text: "Prize 3",
        },
        {
          textFillStyle: "#000",
          fillStyle: "#fadede",
          text: "Prize 4",
        },
        {
          textFillStyle: "#fff",
          fillStyle: "#000",
          text: "Prize 5",
        },
        {
          textFillStyle: "#000",
          fillStyle: "#fadede",
          text: "Prize 6",
        },
        {
          textFillStyle: "#fff",
          fillStyle: "#000",
          text: "Prize 7",
        },
        {
          textFillStyle: "#000",
          fillStyle: "#fadede",
          text: "Prize 8",
        },
      ],
    };
  },
};
</script>
